title: Choose Your Own Star Wars Adventure-1-A New Hope.pdf
description:
Here is the 1st of three Choose Your Own Star Wars Adventure books... released in 1998.  A New Hope, The Empire Strikes Back, and the Return of the Jedi.

These books were released at about the time that Choose Your Own Adventure books stopped being published for many years... Bantam decided to get back in publishing the CYOA books... but they're just a bunch of re-prints with NEW NUMBERS, and The Cave of Time is not #1 any more, The Abominable Snowman is.  Bites Ass, I don't need to collect the new ones for the most part; although I'm glad they're in print again now.

I have all three of the CYOswA books, and I will be releasing them on tpb in the next few days.

Enjoy
